cy, high-alertness alpha or beta states while awake, but it\'s thought possible to induce theta state slower in frequency than alpha and beta through concentration techniques).', 'Làm gì khi có thai', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lam-gi-khi-co-thai', '', '', '2018-05-14 13:50:30', '2018-05-14 06:50:30', '', 0, 'http://td_uid_9_5af67a39124f6', 0, 'post', '', 0),
